Condition_summary_1: The work must be completed by the expiration date or DFO must be notified for extension.
Condition_summary_2: Sediment and erosion control measures must be implemented and monitored, including approved plans and turbidity monitoring.
Condition_summary_3: Offsetting measures include placing course rock substrate to provide 2792 HEUs of habitat.
Condition_summary_4: Monitoring and reporting requirements for offsetting measures over ten years, including photographic records and annual reports.
Habitat_Type: Intertidal marine habitat, Subtidal marine habitat, Intertidal unnamed stream
